{"tid":2317527,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PS5騙案 極賤招扮良心商人！YouTuber受害者和騙子面對面對質 大反擊","createTime":"2020-12-08T15:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T23:40:45.000Z","uid":84882,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"95803991da203b6d0883d1e5caab160385fef5d4","tid":2317527,"uid":84882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">影片第1集：PS5騙案受害經歷 盒中藏著的其實是PS4</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4XXzPpul_A&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4XXzPpul_A%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3Wwi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=a2078146\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4XXzPpul_A&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n11月23日，Roki向觀眾分享，他雖然參加了數次PS5的抽選但全數落選。所以便開始在各大網上購物平台尋找以原價購買PS5的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-12-08-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.41.37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-12-08-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.41.37.jpg&h=39c1e8c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最終，他竟然成功找到一位賣家以原價6萬日圓發售，賣家解釋，因為家人抽到兩部PS5，故將一台放售。他更強調，放售的目的並非高價炒賣，所以原價放售。無論怎樣看也很可疑吧？但Roki對PS5的欲望戰勝了理智，果斷下單。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-12-08-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.42.38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-12-08-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.42.38.jpg&h=79039c6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貨到了，竟然是貨真價實的PS5！！他滿心歡喜開箱，內裹裝着的竟然是一台PS4！！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-12-08-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%881.43.24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-12-08-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25881.43.24.jpg&h=f85942a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">影片第2集：出動私家偵探查案 直搗騙子家對質 掀開騙局</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YywF3MVqWig&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYywF3MVqWig%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3Wwi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=5609b822\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YywF3MVqWig&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\nRoki本身打算就此作罷。但觀眾們紛紛指出，如果就此放過那個騙子，只會令更多人受害。為了完全擊倒這個騙子，Roki雇用私家偵探將他的所有個人資料，如住址、家庭成員、工作等徹底「起底」！一切準備就緒後，他決定直搗騙子的家中質問！<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/-2020-12-08-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%882.48.56-e1607419158779.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F-2020-12-08-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25882.48.56-e1607419158779.jpg&h=9815e49f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRoki先裝作是剛搬到來的鄰戶前來向騙子打招呼，騙得騙子打開門後Roki馬上表明來意，並展示手中的那部假的「PS5」。在門口議論一會後，騙子並不想驚動公寓的其他住客，但因為Roki 掌握了他的所有個人資訊，只好讓Roki進入屋內。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-12-08-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%882.50.33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-12-08-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25882.50.33.jpg&h=9bc1504f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在屋內他繼續否認，甚至將責任推給速遞的人。Roki繼續質問，並開始談及騙子家人的事。他明顯地不想讓家人知道此事，馬上答應可以退款並賠償。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-12-08-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%882.52.47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-12-08-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25882.52.47.jpg&h=23868abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n言談間發現他主力售賣的產品是Switch。初時否認有詐騙其他人。但在Roki的逼問下，他承認有將PS5空盒當作真品賣給客人，難怪他無論如何也不肯讓Roki觸碰櫃子裹的Switch及遊戲吧。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-12-08-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%882.54.35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-12-08-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25882.54.35.jpg&h=ed772a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRoki追問他詐騙他人的原因，他最初說是因為肺炎，工作不順，為了家人才幹起這種事。Roki馬上揭算他的謊言，指他在公司是部長職級， 收入應該相當不錯吧。他才不得不道出真相：因為賭博欠下大量債務，為了不讓家人知道才幹起這種事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-12-08-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%882.56.45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-12-08-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25882.56.45.jpg&h=d17afe42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此時他才誠心道歉，答應退款給其他受害者，以後也不會再幹這種事，並希望Roki不要報警。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2020-12-08-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%885.09.18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2020-12-08-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%25885.09.18.jpg&h=6e7e87ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRoki離開後，前往警署報警，在証據充足的情況下，希望將騙子徹底擊潰，案件亦暫時告一段落。<br />\n<br />\n大家在網上購物都要小心受騙，不要讓騙子有機可乘呢！"},{"pid":"62bff0059d24f092445a3ea39a25ef172e1bfef2","tid":2317